I’m autistic and cannot understand certain things if it’s not explained to me. it could be the most obvious thing in the world, yet I just won’t understand unless it’s explained to me.
I was also under the impression that it was fine for me to just ignore that mal was shipping horus3th as I myself don’t engage in content like that.

the manhwa depicts sa as a bad thing. none of it is ever portrayed in a good manner but that’s just going off of the little bits I read, since it was bad enough for me to have to skip when I’m usually okay with handling heavy topics like these.

it was wrong of me to impulsively tweet about the situation before I fully understood what it was. I first saw it as a personal attack on people who enjoy the manhwa itself and felt quite bad seeing people say that it was “centered around sa and incest” when it isn’t.
first of all, DON’T FUCKING CALL ME A PROSHIPPER. don’t lump me in with or even suggest I’m a proshipper. I am HEAVILY against the “it’s just fiction” belief.
